## Frontend Rules (templates/ only)
- Use Bootstrap 5 classes — do not write custom CSS for layout
- All interactive elements must have accessible labels (aria-label or label element)
- JavaScript goes in <script> tags at the bottom of the body, not inline
- Use fetch() for all async requests — no jQuery
- Every form must have client-side validation before submission
- Data displayed to the user must be HTML-escaped — never inject raw API data into innerHTML